I wholeheartedly agree with the emphasis on human connections in driving scientific innovation and healing. At its core, technology and medicine are not just about cold facts or algorithms; they are deeply personal endeavors that require a shared commitment to improving lives. The interpersonal dynamics within organizations can significantly influence both the speed and impact of breakthroughs.

